Body length 0.8–1.3 mm . Colour dark brown to dark grey. Tegumentary granulation coarse on part of the dorsal side of thoracic terga II–abdominal terga VI. Abdominal tergum V with 12–15 tegumentary granules between setae p 1 . Antennal segment I with seven setae; antennal segment II with 12 setae. Antennal III organ with two sensilla guarded by raised cuticle and two guard sensilla (
Fig. 1
